docs.lead_paragraph: HOLLYWOOD. HER studio once announced that Deanna Durbin would make a picture called "A Queen at Fourteen." The picture never materialized, but the prophecy of its title has been fulfilled by the contract Deanna recently signed. At 16, Deanna is a queen in Hollywood, where royalty is less a matter of Burke than of box office, less of birth than of boodle. She has starred in five pictures in a row.

headline.main: ONE SMART GIRL; By the time Deanna Durbin --"America's Kid Sister"-- is 21 she Will have a cool $1,000,000 in, the bank.
